{
  "stem": "3085.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I say, I probably don't recollect too much about him, because I was a child, and I-- I don't remember an awful lot.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I more or less told you what I remembered about him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I can't say that he did anything terrible to me personally.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I don't think I have any lasting effects of any of the experiments he did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I hope not, and I don't believe I do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I don't recall him ever injecting anything into my body or my brother's body.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I do know about him injecting other kids, and-- and I do know that he did terrible things to other children and other twins.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Basically, I'm lucky.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my brother and I, I think, are basically lucky that nothing-- no permanent damage, certainly not physical permanent damage resulted from his experiments.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't-- I don't-- I didn't have firsthand knowledge of it until actually a few years ago, when the twins had a meeting in Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a get together, and some of them described their-- their experiences.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then that's when I really found out that some of them fared a lot worse than I did, because somehow, in those days, I don't-- I didn't even realize what may have happened to some of the others.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If a pair of twins disappeared suddenly, I probably would've noticed it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if I wasn't close to them, it probably wouldn't have made much difference in those days to me, because we were preoccupied with survival ourselves.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we children didn't have to-- or twins didn't have to work, at least not until the very end.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We sort of had-- we could just sit around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we weren't expected to do any work.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
